{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/Entering.gif?t=1698257356\" /><br><strong>FROM FEAR</strong> is a 1-4 player online co-op survival horror where you choose your fear. Collect resources, unlock new maps and tools, all while trying to stay alive.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CHOOSE YOUR FEAR</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/FearChoice.gif?t=1698257356\" /><br><strong>Fear is personal</strong> - Choose your own and let the game adapt to <strong>your</strong> fear.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Monster and loot determined by fear.<br></li><li> Unique experiences, even across multiplayer.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE MONSTER</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/Monster.gif?t=1698257356\" /><br><strong>Hide from your fear</strong> - Stay out of their way or be hunted down.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unpredictable AI - No game will be the same.<br></li><li> Use the environment to lure the monster.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">COLLECT RESOURCES</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/CollectLoot.gif?t=1698257356\" /><br>Collect resources to unlock new maps and characters.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Items found are broken down into one or more resources.<br></li><li> Find the fuel or remain stranded.<br></li><li> Discover keys to unlock new areas.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">1-4 PLAYER ONLINE CO-OP</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764660/extras/Coop.gif?t=1698257356\" /><br><strong>Face your fears alone or with friends</strong> - Will you help or leave them behind?<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Heal wounded allies or let them bleed out.<br></li><li> When cornered, use your f